OL,5, A job applicant said he received a     
OL,6, "disingenuous and lacklustre" apology  
OL,7, from The Ritz after he was told that   
OL,8, "Afro-style hair" was banned among     
OL,9, staff at the exclusive London hotel.   
OL,11,FJerelle Jules had reached the final    
OL,12,Finterview stage with the hotel when he 
OL,13,Fwas sent its employee grooming policy. 
OL,15,FThe 30-year-old said he was later told 
OL,16,Fthat a black hair stylist from The Ritz
OL,17,Fhad approved the policy phrasing.      
OL,19,FMr Jules said the document indicated   
OL,20,F"institutional racism".                
